Similarly, it is recorded that plant compounds like flavonoids, esters, alkaloids, glycosides, and fatty acids control insects in various ways (
Baz et al . 2021
, 2022b ) as toxicants, feeding deterrents/antifeedants, growth retardants, repellents, chemosterilants, and attractants ( Khater 2012 ; Khater and Geden 2018 ;
Hegazy et al. 2022
